title: Bug 4121 - JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
description: The JarExporter is causing an out of sync issue.
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar file in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself to avoid the out of sync message.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Place the exported jar file in the same directory (project).
3. Overwrite the exported jar file for the second time.
Expected result: No out of sync message should be displayed.
